CT,20,T
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1778771469
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G3/3
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 29 May to Fri 12 Jun
OL,6,FWhilst further rain and showers are
OL,7,Fpossible at times, there is also
OL,8,Flikely to be spells of fine and dry
OL,9,Fweather. Patterns which bring more
OL,10,Fsettled weather are more likely to
OL,11,Fdominate towards the end of May across
OL,12,Fsouthern areas with more unsettled
OL,13,Fspells of weather likely to be focused
OL,14,Ffurther north. Into June, more mixed
OL,15,Fconditions are likely with spells of
OL,16,Frain and showers, but also some drier
OL,17,Fweather at times. Temperatures are
OL,18,Fmost likely to be near or slightly
OL,19,Fabove average overall, with some warm
OL,20,Fweather possible at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
